news.title: Home Depot earnings beat Wall Street estimates, as retailer breaks comparable sales losing streak
news.summary: Home Depot narrowly beat fourth-quarter earnings estimates, but it gave lackluster sales guidance. High interest rates and home prices pose challenges, Home Depot says.

news.title: PayPal lays out strategy for Venmo to reach $2 billion in revenue in 2027
news.summary: PayPal is focused on expanding Venmo’s role in digital commerce. Facing competitors like Cash App, Zelle, and Apple Pay, PayPal is focusing on Venmo.

news.title: How digitally native companies like Rothy's are growing profitably in a new era for retail
news.summary: Rothy's is growing profitably after expanding into wholesale and building its store fleet. In 2024, it saw sales grow 17%. In 2015, Rothy's saw sales growth of 17%.

news.title: Trump says tariffs on Canada and Mexico 'will go forward'
news.summary: President Donald Trump says sweeping tariffs on Canada and Mexico "will go forward" A monthlong delay on their implementation expires next week. President Donald Trump said sweeping tariffs will go forward.

news.title: Nvida to report earnings amid infrastructure spending, DeepSeek concerns
news.summary: Nvidia reports fourth-quarter financial results on Wednesday after the bell. Nvidia is the world's largest graphics chip maker. The company also has a dominant market share in the PC and tablet market.

news.title: Eli Lilly cuts price of weight-loss drug Zepbound for self-paying patients
news.summary: The drug company is calling on insurers and federal programs to include coverage of obesity as a chronic disease. The company is also calling on the federal government to include obesity in its health insurance plans.

news.title: There are dot-com echoes beyond tech. This Costco shareholder explains why returns will be paltry at best.
news.summary: A fund manager says there are parallels between now and the 1998-to-2000 period, and not just in the megacap tech stocks.

news.title: Novo Nordisk’s stock is rallying as Hims & Hers’ stock falters. An Ozempic alternative won’t be available for long.
news.summary: Novo Nordisk shares rallied on Tuesday as a maker of a weight-loss drug alternative confirmed it won't be selling it for much longer.

news.title: No ‘golden age’ is coming. Trump’s tariffs will hit Americans with higher interest rates and more inflation.
news.summary: Protectionism won’t make us rich, especially if tariffs launch a trade war, writes CNN’s John Sutter. Sutter: “I’m worried that we’re going to have to get used to the idea of tariffs.”
